# VHS Tape — When Claudes Meet
# https://github.com/charmbracelet/vhs

Output replay.gif
Output replay.mp4

Set Shell zsh
Set FontSize 18
Set Width 1200
Set Height 700
Set Padding 20
Set Theme "Molokai"
Set TypingSpeed 0ms
Set PlaybackSpeed 1

Hide
Type "clear"
Enter
Sleep 0.5s
Show
Type "python3 /Users/anadim/when-claudes-meet/replay.py"
Enter
Sleep 200s
